Clinical Team Searches - Departmental Breakdown

This circle packing chart shows the relative frequency of search requests per deparment affiliation of the requester, and how this departmental affiliation points back to its larger categorical group (YNHH, YSPH, YSM, Other, etc.).

Click on the circles within the plot in order to zoom in and see further detail.
